DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
8409::$$$message_0083_0000_0000$$$::I'm worried about Sakura.[lr]::
8410::$$$message_0083_0000_0001$$$::Nothing will come from me worrying about her, but I should at least check to see if she's perked up.::
8411::$$$message_0083_0001_0000$$$::I walk through the first year's hall, which is on the fourth floor.[lr]::
8412::$$$message_0083_0001_0001$$$::There aren't any students walking down the hall, and there's only a handful of students hanging around the classroom.[lr]::
8413::$$$message_0083_0001_0002$$$::They're either at their clubs or headed home.::
8414::$$$message_0083_0002_0000$$$::"Damn. Sakura's probably at her club too."[lr]::
8415::$$$message_0083_0002_0001$$$::Well, I've come this far.[lr]::
8416::$$$message_0083_0002_0002$$$::I might as well check Sakura's classroom, and after I see that nobody's there, I'll head to work.::
8417::$$$message_0083_0003_0000$$$::"Let's see."[lr]::
8418::$$$message_0083_0003_0001$$$::I peek into class 1-B.[lr]::
8419::$$$message_0083_0003_0002$$$::The classroom is tinted red from the light of the setting sun pouring in through the windows. It's silent, giving the impression nobody is inside.::
8420::$$$message_0083_0004_0000$$$::There doesn't seem to be anybody in the classroom.[lr]::
8421::$$$message_0083_0004_0001$$$::All the students have gone to their respective destinations.[lr]::
8422::$$$message_0083_0004_0002$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
8423::$$$message_0083_0004_0003$$$::Except for one lone shadow that remained inside the red-soaked classroom. ::
8424::$$$message_0083_0005_0000$$$::"Sakura."[lr]::
8425::$$$message_0083_0005_0001$$$::I step into the crimson-tinted world and say her name.::
8426::$$$message_0083_0006_0000$$$::"...Senpai?"[lr]::
8427::$$$message_0083_0006_0001$$$::Her long hair is covering her face, but she looks even more weary than this morning.::
8428::$$$message_0083_0007_0000$$$::"Is something wrong? Do you need anything from our classroom?"[lr]::
8429::$$$message_0083_0007_0001$$$::"No, I didn't come to check on your classroom. I was just worried about you, since you seemed down this morning."::
8430::$$$message_0083_0008_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
8431::$$$message_0083_0008_0001$$$::Sakura's face grows, if possible, even more downcast.[lr]::
8432::$$$message_0083_0008_0002$$$::She's obviously not well.::
8433::$$$message_0083_0009_0000$$$::"Sakura, you should go home if you don't feel well. I can at least walk you to the intersection, so let's go home."::
8434::$$$message_0083_0010_0000$$$::"...No, it's fine. I'm not sick.[lr]::
8435::$$$message_0083_0010_0001$$$::I'm going to my club like always, then I'll have dinner with you after my club.[lr]::
8436::$$$message_0083_0010_0002$$$::...There is nothing wrong. So please don't worry."[lr]::
8437::$$$message_0083_0010_0003$$$::She grabs her bag and starts walking so quickly it's almost as if she's trying to run away.::
8438::$$$message_0083_0011_0000$$$::"Dummy. You don't look well enough to say that. Just don't go to your club today. Besides, you won't be able to draw your bow properly, the way you are right now."[lr]::
8439::$$$message_0083_0011_0001$$$::I grab Sakura's hand as she tries to pass me.::
8440::$$$message_0083_0012_0000$$$::"Oh..."[lr]::
8441::$$$message_0083_0012_0001$$$::A loud "thud" echoes through the classroom.[lr]::
8442::$$$message_0083_0012_0002$$$::Sakura almost falls, even though I only tried grabbing her hand.[lr]::
8443::$$$message_0083_0012_0003$$$::"Hey...!"[lr]::
8444::$$$message_0083_0012_0004$$$::I quickly pull Sakura's arm.[lr]::
8445::$$$message_0083_0012_0005$$$::As I tug Sakura so firmly, I learn she is surprisingly light.::
8446::$$$message_0083_0013_0000$$$::"Y-you gave me a scare there. Are you sure you're all right?[lr]::
8447::$$$message_0083_0013_0001$$$::You didn't put any weight into your step."[lr]::
8448::$$$message_0083_0013_0002$$$::"..."[lr]::
8449::$$$message_0083_0013_0003$$$::Sakura averts her eyes apologetically.[lr]::
8450::$$$message_0083_0013_0004$$$::Honestly, what's gotten into her today?::
8451::$$$message_0083_0014_0000$$$::"You're not going to your club today. I won't go to work either, so let's just go home."[lr]::
8452::$$$message_0083_0014_0001$$$::"..."[lr]::
8453::$$$message_0083_0014_0002$$$::Sakura doesn't respond, keeping quiet.[lr]::
8454::$$$message_0083_0014_0003$$$::She doesn't shake off my hand, nor does it look like she's going to listen to me.::
8455::$$$message_0083_0015_0000$$$::"What's going on, Sakura? You know you're in no shape to go to your club today."[lr]::
8456::$$$message_0083_0015_0001$$$::"...Y-you're right. But my brother is waiting."[lr]::
8457::$$$message_0083_0015_0002$$$::"Which is why I need to go," she adds almost inaudibly.::
8458::$$$message_0083_0016_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
8459::$$$message_0083_0016_0001$$$::Damn.[lr]::
8460::$$$message_0083_0016_0002$$$::I never have any reply to that look.[lr]::
8461::$$$message_0083_0016_0003$$$::I hear the Matou family's circumstances are...complicated, and I can't really put myself in the middle of Shinji and Sakura.::
8462::$$$message_0083_0017_0000$$$::No matter how much I consider Sakura my family, the people in the Matou household are her real family.[lr]::
8463::$$$message_0083_0017_0001$$$::As an outsider, my words will fall on deaf ears. Anything I said would just seem like unnecessary meddling.::
8464::$$$message_0083_0018_0000$$$::"So you're still going to stop by the club, Sakura?"[lr]::
8465::$$$message_0083_0018_0001$$$::"Eh? Oh, yes. I do realize I'm in no state to draw a bow."::
8466::$$$message_0083_0019_0000$$$::"Yeah. So you're just going there to save face for Shinji." [lr]::
8467::$$$message_0083_0019_0001$$$::I pull out a chair and sit on it.[lr]::
8468::$$$message_0083_0019_0002$$$::Then I pull another chair from the neighboring desk.::
8469::$$$message_0083_0020_0000$$$::"Um...Senpai?"[lr]::
8470::$$$message_0083_0020_0001$$$::"Just sit down. I'm not going to stop you from going to the club anymore, but just take a minute to rest, okay? You can tell Shinji you're late because I held you back."::
8471::$$$message_0083_0021_0000$$$::"I-I can't say that! If I do, my brother might do something to you...again..."::
8472::$$$message_0083_0022_0000$$$::"Shinji giving me a hard time is nothing new.[lr]::
8473::$$$message_0083_0022_0001$$$::Don't worry about it. I bet it makes his life easier if he has something new to bring up.[lr]::
8474::$$$message_0083_0022_0002$$$::Besides, telling him that I held you back wouldn't be a flat-out lie. It's absolutely true. There's nothing to feel guilty about."[lr]::
8475::$$$message_0083_0022_0003$$$::I gesture for Sakura to sit down.::
8476::$$$message_0083_0023_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
8477::$$$message_0083_0023_0001$$$::Sakura reluctantly sits on the chair.::
8478::$$$message_0083_0024_0000$$$::"Good. Now hold on a minute. I'm going to steal some tea from the student council room. You stay right there until I get back."::
8479::$$$message_0083_0025_0000$$$::"Eh? Steal some tea? Won't you get in trouble for that?"::
8480::$$$message_0083_0026_0000$$$::"Only if a teacher catches me. I'm used to things like this. It won't be an issue as long as I don't run into a teacher, so just sit back and relax."[lr]::
8481::$$$message_0083_0026_0001$$$::"I-I can't do that! Especially knowing you're going to do something risky. Senpai, please don't worry about getting tea for me!"::
8482::$$$message_0083_0027_0000$$$::"And I keep saying it's not risky. Just sit there, okay? Drinking tea in the classroom is good for you once in a while."[lr]::
8483::$$$message_0083_0027_0001$$$::"Oh."::
8484::$$$message_0083_0028_0000$$$::I jump out into the hallway.[lr]::
8485::$$$message_0083_0028_0001$$$::The student council room isn't that far.[lr]::
8486::$$$message_0083_0028_0002$$$::I'll go get a whole tea set real quick to surprise Sakura.::
8487::$$$message_0083_0029_0000$$$::...Time passes.[lr]::
8488::$$$message_0083_0029_0001$$$::Sakura and I both drink tea in the classroom, which seems ludicrous, but we look out the window as we have nothing better to do.[lr]::
8489::$$$message_0083_0029_0002$$$::The last rays of the sunset filter in through the window, stinging my eyes a bit.::
8490::$$$message_0083_0030_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
8491::$$$message_0083_0030_0001$$$::Sakura looks toward the sunset, her expression vacant.[lr]::
8492::$$$message_0083_0030_0002$$$::I don't have much to say, so I follow Sakura and keep my mouth shut.::
8493::$$$message_0083_0031_0000$$$::Since there's no conversation, time passes slowly.[lr]::
8494::$$$message_0083_0031_0001$$$::Sakura's not generally all that talkative, and it's not unusual for her to just stare blankly ahead.[lr]::
8495::$$$message_0083_0031_0002$$$::She seems to be more at ease when she's alone.[lr]::
8496::$$$message_0083_0031_0003$$$::Come to think of it, Sakura prefers to be alone.[lr]::
8497::$$$message_0083_0031_0004$$$::It's not that she wants to be away from the hustle and bustle, so much as her seeming to want to be isolated from the people around her, and she often chooses to look outside rather than keeping her attention inside.::
8498::$$$message_0083_0032_0000$$$::...Which is probably why she stayed alone in the classroom today.[lr]::
8499::$$$message_0083_0032_0001$$$::Sakura doesn't go out of her way to interact with people.[lr]::
8500::$$$message_0083_0032_0002$$$::Fuji-nee and I are the exceptions.[lr]::
8501::$$$message_0083_0032_0003$$$::And if I weren't acquaintances with Shinji, Sakura wouldn't have had to interact with me at all really.::
8502::$$$message_0083_0033_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
8503::$$$message_0083_0033_0001$$$::I sneak a glace at Sakura.[lr]::
8504::$$$message_0083_0033_0002$$$::Four years ago, when Shinji introduced me to her, Sakura seemed more like a little girl.[lr]::
8505::$$$message_0083_0033_0003$$$::Before I knew it, she was my underclassman, and even started coming to my house to help with housework, and her childish appearance started to fade.::
8506::$$$message_0083_0034_0000$$$::Sakura has become beautiful.[lr]::
8507::$$$message_0083_0034_0001$$$::Well, she was pretty to begin with, but I guess I'd say she's grown...[font italic=true]too[font italic=false] pretty.[lr]::
8508::$$$message_0083_0034_0002$$$::On top of that, she's sensible, and so gentle.[lr]::
8509::$$$message_0083_0034_0003$$$::With all those great qualities, it's no wonder so many people say she's a beauty on par with Rin Tohsaka.::
8510::$$$message_0083_0035_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
8511::$$$message_0083_0035_0001$$$::But there's something I just don't get.[lr]::
8512::$$$message_0083_0035_0002$$$::Sakura is often alone.[lr]::
8513::$$$message_0083_0035_0003$$$::She doesn't seem to have any friends from the kyudou club, and given that she was alone in the classroom after school, she may not have any friends in her class either.::
8514::$$$message_0083_0036_0000$$$::Now that I think about it, I only know the Sakura from the kyudou club and the Sakura at my house.[lr]::
8515::$$$message_0083_0036_0001$$$::I don't know what Sakura does or how she acts when she's at school, or the Matou family home.::
8516::$$$message_0083_0037_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
8517::$$$message_0083_0037_0001$$$::Just when I realize that, and as I continued to stare blankly at the reddened sky...[lr]::
8518::$$$message_0083_0037_0002$$$::"Senpai, do you remember?"[lr]::
8519::$$$message_0083_0037_0003$$$::Sakura asks, without taking her gaze from the window.::
8520::$$$message_0083_0038_0000$$$::"Remember what?"[lr]::
8521::$$$message_0083_0038_0001$$$::"From long ago. When I didn't know you yet."[lr]::
8522::$$$message_0083_0038_0002$$$::"So before you and I met?"::
8523::$$$message_0083_0039_0000$$$::"Yes. Four years ago, when I'd just started school.[lr]::
8524::$$$message_0083_0039_0001$$$::I had yet to get accustomed to school, and as I was aimlessly walking down the hall, I saw something very strange."::
8525::$$$message_0083_0040_0000$$$::"I really don't know how things unfolded back then, honestly...[lr]::
8526::$$$message_0083_0040_0001$$$::But it was after school, and members of the track team had left already. Yet there was one person still out there running. And as I continued to watch, he started doing high jumps."::
8527::$$$message_0083_0041_0000$$$::She giggles.[lr]::
8528::$$$message_0083_0041_0001$$$::It must be an endearing memory to Sakura, if that blissful smile is anything to go by.::
8529::$$$message_0083_0042_0000$$$::"The entire school was painted red by the sunset, and it was beautiful but it also made me feel lonesome.[lr]::
8530::$$$message_0083_0042_0001$$$::And all that time, this person continued to practice alone. They would run, jump, drop their pole, and repeat that step. There was nobody around, and they clearly couldn't actually manage the height they were attempting. But they kept trying nonetheless."::
8531::$$$message_0083_0043_0000$$$::"It wasn't a matter of trying, because that pole was much taller than this person.[lr]::
8532::$$$message_0083_0043_0001$$$::Even I could tell it was impossible, and that person must have known it too."::
8533::$$$message_0083_0044_0000$$$::"What?"[lr]::
8534::$$$message_0083_0044_0001$$$::I understand the story, but I'm not sure what she's getting at.[lr]::
8535::$$$message_0083_0044_0002$$$::I don't think grueling solo practice after school is all that strange.::
8536::$$$message_0083_0045_0000$$$::"I was a bad girl at that moment. Something was bothering me, and I wanted to vent my anger on someone. So I was watching this person, and the entire time I was wishing for them to fail, to give up...and I wanted to see the moment their determination failed.[lr]::
8537::$$$message_0083_0045_0001$$$::But it didn't happen.[lr]::
8538::$$$message_0083_0045_0002$$$::I watched this person attempt to do the impossible many times, to the point their tenacity grew frightening. They never once complained."::
8539::$$$message_0083_0046_0000$$$::"Huh. They must've been desperate. Maybe there were tryouts the next day, and they needed to be able to reach that height to make the cut."::
8540::$$$message_0083_0047_0000$$$::"No, that wasn't it. See, they weren't even a member of the track and field club."[lr]::
8541::$$$message_0083_0047_0001$$$::Huh.[lr]::
8542::$$$message_0083_0047_0002$$$::But why is Sakura laughing?::
8543::$$$message_0083_0048_0000$$$::"And then, I realized something as I was watching. It didn't matter what this person was doing. They just happened to find something they couldn't do today, and they were stubborn enough not to give up.[lr]::
8544::$$$message_0083_0048_0001$$$::And so after the sun set, this person put all the equipment away alone and went home. They must have been exhausted, but they left calmly, like nothing had happened."::
8545::$$$message_0083_0049_0000$$$::"I don't get it. If they left, they must have succeeded, right? How tall was that pole anyway?"::
8546::$$$message_0083_0050_0000$$$::"Hehe. Well, the thing is, they didn't actually manage it after all. They finally concluded that they couldn't jump it after three hours of trying."[lr]::
8547::$$$message_0083_0050_0001$$$::"Whoa, not exactly a happy ending."::
8548::$$$message_0083_0051_0000$$$::"Yes. This person was so earnest that I even worried about them.[lr]::
8549::$$$message_0083_0051_0001$$$::And I figured they had to be dependable.[lr]::
8550::$$$message_0083_0051_0002$$$::But that also made me feel uneasy and lonely."[lr]::
8551::$$$message_0083_0051_0003$$$::Sakura sounds so lonely as she says that, and I'm afraid she could be entirely swallowed up in the red classroom.::
8552::$$$message_0083_0052_0000$$$::"Huh. Well, now that you've told me the whole story...what's it about, Sakura?"[lr]::
8553::$$$message_0083_0052_0001$$$::"No, it's fine if you don't understand. I was just telling you how I felt when I saw it. But I have a feeling that was just a typical day for that person."[lr]::
8554::$$$message_0083_0052_0002$$$::Sakura smiles warmly, seeming to have come out of her dark mood from earlier.::
8555::$$$message_0083_0053_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
8556::$$$message_0083_0053_0001$$$::Just then...[lr]::
8557::$$$message_0083_0053_0002$$$::I may be dense, but I realize who she's talking about.[lr]::
8558::$$$message_0083_0053_0003$$$::I actually don't remember it happening, but if it's a story from four years ago, it must've been a little after my old man died.[lr]::
8559::$$$message_0083_0053_0004$$$::I did some pretty reckless stuff every day, so I guess Sakura's story is just one instance of that.::
8560::$$$message_0083_0054_0000$$$::"Uh...Sakura. Don't tell me that person's..."[lr]::
8561::$$$message_0083_0054_0001$$$::"Yes. The story's about an upperclassman. In fact, he's in the room with me right now.[lr]::
8562::$$$message_0083_0054_0002$$$::You were a little smaller back then, so I thought you were in the same grade as me."[lr]::
8563::$$$message_0083_0054_0003$$$::Ugh.[lr]::
8564::$$$message_0083_0054_0004$$$::I really wish she wouldn't bring up my height when I was younger.[lr]::
8565::$$$message_0083_0054_0005$$$::Sure, I'm not that tall even now, but I still had a growth spurt.::
8566::$$$message_0083_0055_0000$$$::"That's what I mean. I knew you, even back then."[lr]::
8567::$$$message_0083_0055_0001$$$::"I-I see. That's news to me."[lr]::
8568::$$$message_0083_0055_0002$$$::I look away, embarrassed that she saw me in such an awkward moment.::
8569::$$$message_0083_0056_0000$$$::And then...[lr]::
8570::$$$message_0083_0056_0001$$$::"Well, we both saw the same thing back then."[lr]::
8571::$$$message_0083_0056_0002$$$::Sakura gestures like she's praying, and I'm not sure I understand what she's getting at.::
8572::$$$message_0083_0057_0000$$$::"Huh?"[lr]::
8573::$$$message_0083_0057_0001$$$::I ask, feeling concerned.[lr]::
8574::$$$message_0083_0057_0002$$$::But at that moment, the familiar school bell sounds, as if to deny my curiosity.::
8575::$$$message_0083_0058_0000$$$::"Hey, the bell rang."[lr]::
8576::$$$message_0083_0058_0001$$$::It's been thirty minutes since I had her stay in the classroom with me. The time is half past four.[lr]::
8577::$$$message_0083_0058_0002$$$::"I guess holding you back longer wouldn't do. I'll clean up so you can go ahead. You feel better, right?"::
8578::$$$message_0083_0059_0000$$$::"Yes, I feel much better thanks to you. Please look forward to dinner tonight."[lr]::
8579::$$$message_0083_0059_0001$$$::Sakura gets up.[lr]::
8580::$$$message_0083_0059_0002$$$::She doesn't seem like she's forcing it; she really does look better.::
8581::$$$message_0083_0060_0000$$$::"Oh sorry, Sakura. I actually need to work tonight. I'm going to be late, so you don't have to worry about taking the time to go to my house tonight."[lr]::
8582::$$$message_0083_0060_0001$$$::"Understood. Then I'll just make dinner and leave it for you."[lr]::
8583::$$$message_0083_0060_0002$$$::Sakura quickly bows and leaves.::
8584::$$$message_0083_0061_0000$$$::"Oh well."[lr]::
8585::$$$message_0083_0061_0001$$$::Fuji-nee should be at my place, so she should be able to walk Sakura home when it's time.[lr]::
8586::$$$message_0083_0061_0002$$$::My livelihood's at stake too, so I better head over to work quickly.::

